snippet.title: Pizza Party Pickup Gameplay - (Suite Life of Zack and Cody) Online Disney Channel
snippet.description:
WHO REMEMBERS THIS GAME? I DOOOOO!!! I missed the Disney Channel games soo much that of course I uploaded a gameplay video from this iconic game. When I was a kid I almost NEVER got passed level 7, and as you can see at 19 years old I still fail miserably. Hope this brings back some good memories for you all!

Enjoy!

--stripes
